            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "text": "{\"result\":{\"asin\":\"B0GHWTJ5K8\",\"imageUrl\":\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/41HTHkRXrvL._SS180_.jpg\",\"productTitle\":\"Hilldow 6V 1700mAh NiMH Receiver RX Battery High Capacity Rechargeable Battery Pack with BBL2/Hitec Plug for RC Airplanes Aircrafts\",\"featureBullets\":[\"【1700mAh NiMH Battery Specification】- Battery Voltage: 6V; Capacity: 1700mAh; ; Connector Type: BBL2/Hitec Connector.\",\"【Dimensions of the NiMh battery】: 6V 1700mah NiMH battery; Size: 5*3.2*3.1cm/1.97*1.26*1.22inch ; Single battery weight: 125g/4.41oz\",\"High Capacity Rechargeable Power: Features 1700mAh capacity providing extended runtime for your RC aircraft and airplane applications with reliable rechargeable NiMH technology\",\"Compatible Connector Type: Equipped with BBL2/Hitec plug connectors ensuring secure and reliable connection to your RC receiver system for consistent power delivery\",\"【Safety Warning】- 1. Please read the user instruction manual before use of the battery.2. Please use Professional NiMH battery charger. 3. The suggested charging rate is 0.5 - 1C. 4. Never charge the battery unattended.\",\"What Included: 6V 1700mAh NiMH Battery*1\"],\"byLineContributors\":[\"Hilldow\"],\"catalogSize\":null,\"taxCurrency\":\"USD\",\"taxValue\":19.99,\"promotionId\":\"A2MSI1YDV1P2LP\",\"purchasePolicyCode\":\"AmazonVine\",\"asinTangoEligible\":true,\"productSiteLaunchDate\":1768969138605,\"limitedQuantity\":false},\"error\":null}"
          },
