          "content": {
            "size": 1961,
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "text": "{\"result\":{\"asin\":\"B0GRGX53LT\",\"imageUrl\":\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/41zJtxZv3XL._SS180_.jpg\",\"productTitle\":\"ABCPXY Soccer Jersey National Flag Short Sleeve Graphic Men Sport T-Shirt Unisex Training Football Top Game Day Outfit (Medium, Mexico)\",\"featureBullets\":[\"Soft and Comfortable Fabric：Made from premium polyester, this fabric is soft, smooth, and comfortable against the skin, while also offering excellent durability for everyday wear. Even after repeated washing, the fabric retains its shape and color, making it ideal for sports, training, or casual activities.\",\"Breathable Unisex Athletic Fit：This unisex athletic t-shirt features a relaxed, athletic fit for comfort and flexibility. Whether you're heading to football practice, running errands, traveling, or relaxing with friends, it's a comfortable and stylish everyday workout outfit.\",\"Summer Wear：This lightweight football t-shirt is ideal for summer wear. Easily pair it with athletic shorts, jeans, jogging pants, or casual pants for a sporty-casual look. Perfect for warm weather activities, outdoor sports, beach vacations, travel, or everyday summer wear.\",\"Occasion：Whether watching a football match, supporting your favorite team, playing with friends, attending a sporting event, or simply for casual wear, this versatile football jersey-style T-shirt easily pairs with various outfits to create a vibrant, sporty look.\",\"Easy Care：Sizes S-2XL are available for men and women. Please refer to the size chart before ordering to select the most suitable size. Machine washable or hand wash cold; wash with other clothes of the same color and avoid high temperatures to maintain fabric quality and print.\"],\"byLineContributors\":[\"ABCPXY\"],\"catalogSize\":\"Medium\",\"taxCurrency\":\"USD\",\"taxValue\":19.99,\"promotionId\":\"A2O9DTWD32FQAO\",\"purchasePolicyCode\":\"AmazonVine\",\"asinTangoEligible\":true,\"productSiteLaunchDate\":1772791201910,\"limitedQuantity\":false},\"error\":null}"
          },
