          "content": {
            "size": 3616,
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "text": "{\"result\":{\"asin\":\"B0G6K5S93C\",\"imageUrl\":\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/41+8sPku6vL._SS180_.jpg\",\"productTitle\":\"The 4687EA2001T drain motor pump is compatible with LG washing machines and can replace 4681EA2001D, AP5328388, 4681EA1007G and 2003273.\",\"featureBullets\":[\"I. Preparations Before Disassembly 1. Turn off the power of the washing machine and unplug it to ensure the power is cut off and avoid the risk of electric shock. 2. Prepare the following tools: a Phillips screwdriver, a flat-head screwdriver, a container for water, and a rag (to catch any remaining water). 3. If there is still water in the washing machine, drain it through the low position of the drain pipe first to reduce the overflow of water during disassembly.\",\"II. Disassembly of the Old Drainage Pump 1. Locate the drain pump: It is usually on the right/left side at the bottom of the washing machine. For some models, you need to remove the bottom decorative panel first (unscrew the panel with a screwdriver). 2. Disconnect the drain pipe: Loosen the rubber drain pipe clamp connecting the drain pump and the inner drum of the washing machine by hand, pull out the drain pipe, and direct the remaining water into a container.\",\"3. Unplug the wiring terminals: Remember the connection position of the wires and the drain pump (you can take a photo for record), and unplug the power connection plug (for some models, it is a snap-on type, just press lightly to remove). 4. Remove the fixing screws: Use a cross-head screwdriver to remove the fixing screws of the drain pump (usually 2-3 screws), hold the pump body and gently pull it outwards, and the old drain pump can be removed.\",\"4681EA2001T Drainage Pump Motor, compatible with model AP5328388, is specially designed for installation in front-loading washing machines. The product has been upgraded and optimized. The pump body is crack-resistant and the impeller is of high strength, making it far more durable than ordinary models. It can withstand heavy and overloaded washing conditions and operates stably without faults. The operation noise is low, effectively optimizing the working noise of the washing machine. The installation process is simple and does not require complex tools. It is compatible with multiple front-loading models of LG and other brands, stable, reliable and easy to operate.\",\"Blutoget 4681EA2001T Kenmore washing machine drain pump motor, risk-free shopping, super reassuring! Made of high-quality materials and upgraded materials, it is durable and reliable for long-term use, compatible with LG drain pump AP5328388. 365-day after-sales service guarantees your satisfaction every time you shop. Whether it's this drain pump or related issues for LG washing machines compatible with model 4681EA1007G, feel free to contact customer service at any time. We will do our best to help you solve all problems and ensure your satisfaction.\",\"4681EA2001T washing machine drain pump motor, compatible with LG and Kenmore washing machines, with extremely strong compatibility! It can replace multiple parts such as 4681EA1007D, 4681EA1007G, AP5328388, etc., including over ten types of numbers such as 4681EA2001D/N/U, 2003273, PS3579318, etc. Not sure if it's compatible with your model? Feel free to contact us at any time, and we'll do our best to help you solve the compatibility issue.\"],\"byLineContributors\":[\"ZANBWGQD\"],\"catalogSize\":null,\"taxCurrency\":\"USD\",\"taxValue\":19.88,\"promotionId\":\"A43HF6KRR0955\",\"purchasePolicyCode\":\"AmazonVine\",\"asinTangoEligible\":true,\"productSiteLaunchDate\":1765521965605,\"limitedQuantity\":false},\"error\":null}"
          },
