            "size": 1619,
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "text": "{\"result\":{\"asin\":\"B0GK22TZ9G\",\"imageUrl\":\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/21E1SaQUZIL._SS180_.jpg\",\"productTitle\":\"KIBOVAMO SPX1091G Butterfly Gasket Replacement for Hayward Skimmer - Fits SP1091LX, SP1091WM & Dyna-Skim Above Ground Pool Skimmers\",\"featureBullets\":[\"【SPX1091G Exact Fit Models】 Direct replacement butterfly gasket for SP1091LX, SP1091WM and Dyna-Skim above ground pool skimmers. Perfect dimensional fit, no trimming or modification needed for seamless installation\",\"【Superior Airtight Sealing Performance】 Premium rubber construction creates a watertight seal for skimmer faceplates, stopping water leaks and preventing air infiltration. Maintains optimal skimming efficiency and pool water balance\",\"Engineered to withstand harsh pool chemicals, sunlight and outdoor exposure. Resists cracking, warping and hardening over time—far more durable than standard replacement gaskets\",\"【Tool-Free Quick Installation】 No special tools or professional skills required. Simply remove the old gasket, press the new SPX1091G into place and reattach the skimmer faceplate—installs in minutes for DIY pool owners\",\"【Exclusive for Above Ground Pool Skimmers】 Custom designed for Hayward above ground pool skimmer systems (SP1091LX/SP1091WM). Essential replacement part to restore skimmer functionality and avoid costly pool damage\"],\"byLineContributors\":[\"KIBOVAMO\"],\"catalogSize\":null,\"taxCurrency\":\"USD\",\"taxValue\":12.99,\"promotionId\":\"A3M1ACP4YSYW2X\",\"purchasePolicyCode\":\"AmazonVine\",\"asinTangoEligible\":true,\"productSiteLaunchDate\":1769513977488,\"limitedQuantity\":false},\"error\":null}"
          },
