          "content": {
            "size": 1932,
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "text": "{\"result\":{\"asin\":\"B0GQ2W9VYR\",\"imageUrl\":\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/31qlysrIP9L._SS180_.jpg\",\"productTitle\":\"FizzCove Universal Replacement Pool Hose Adapter - Fits Both 1-1/4\\\" and 1-1/2\\\" Hose Connections - Compatible with Intex Above Ground Pool Pumps, Filters& Saltwater Systems (A-Adapter) (A-Adapter)\",\"featureBullets\":[\"\\uD83C\\uDFAF UNIVERSAL FIT & 4-PACK VALUE SET - Our FizzCove adapter set features a smart dual-end design with 1-1/2\\\" threaded connections on one side, seamlessly adapting to both 1-1/4\\\" and 1-1/2\\\" pool hoses.\",\"\\uD83D\\uDD04 MULTI-APPLICATION VERSATILITY FOR YOUR ENTIRE POOL SYSTEM - Engineered with standard 1-1/2\\\" MIP connection threads, these robust adapters fit perfectly onto most above-ground pool pumps, filters, skimmers, chlorine feeders, and other essential equipment.\",\"\\uD83D\\uDD27 DIRECT REPLACEMENT FOR HAYWARD & MAJOR BRAND COMPATIBILITY - FizzCove adapters serve as direct, high-quality replacements for Hayward SPX1091Z7 and SPX1091Z4 hose adapters Beyond Hayward, these adapters work seamlessly with Intex, Coleman, Bestway, and other leading pool equipment brands.\",\"\\uD83D\\uDCAA SOLVES COMMON HOSE CONNECTION FRUSTRATIONS PERMANENTLY - Our heavy-duty inlet and outlet hose adapters are specifically engineered to solve the most common pool hose compatibility issues. The precision-molded construction ensures tight, secure fits that prevent leaks and maintain optimal water pressure.\",\"\\uD83D\\uDEE0️ PREMIUM DURABILITY & PRO-GRADE INSTALLATION TIPS - Suitable for all age groups from teen pool helpers to senior homeowners, the straightforward installation requires no special tools or plumbing expertise.\"],\"byLineContributors\":[\"FizzCove\"],\"catalogSize\":\"1-1/4\",\"taxCurrency\":\"USD\",\"taxValue\":12.99,\"promotionId\":\"A23Z2I152TPKTW\",\"purchasePolicyCode\":\"AmazonVine\",\"asinTangoEligible\":true,\"productSiteLaunchDate\":1771997356156,\"limitedQuantity\":false},\"error\":null}"
          },
